      "content": {
        "title": "Femoral Neck Fracture Classification",
        "definition": "Garden and Pauwels classifications describing displacement and shear angle of femoral neck fractures.",
        "summary": "Displaced fractures in elderly often treated with arthroplasty; young patients need anatomic fixation."
